data.description: Move-In Ready! Assumable VA Loan at 3.25% (With $286,000 cash at closing).  Charming home situated on a quiet road in the prestigious golf club community of North Hampton. Kitchen and living area are the ideal place for entertaining! Kitchen features updated cabinets, appliances, stone backsplash, and dining area. Spacious living room opens to a covered back porch with serene views of the lagoon!  Large master suite boasts double walk-in closets, garden tub, and ceramic tile floor. Crown molding throughout. Updated Laundry room includes washer and dryer! Well maintained lawn has sprinkler system and the drive way is extra long to provide plenty of off street parking.   Community amenities include pool, splash park, club house, tennis courts, b-ball courts, soccer field, playground, public golf course, outpost with screened in pavilion and kayak launch. HOA dues include internet, security and cable. Call today for a private tour of your new home!
